{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f2fa2d3d9e","title":"对一篇关于人道主义文章的摘报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e8c011c29","index":0,"year":1961,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"17d761caab","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这首诗写毛泽东对湖南的怀念和祝愿。友人即周世钊。本诗毛泽东手迹原题为“答周世钊同学”，后改为“答友人”。周世钊（1897—1976），湖南宁乡人，是毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校的同学，曾加入新民学会。当时任湖南省副省长。解放后与毛泽东信件来往颜多，并有诗词唱和。1961年12月26日毛泽东给周的信中，在引用“秋风万里芙蓉国，春雨千家薛荔村”“西南云气开衡岳，日夜江声下洞庭”（岳麓山联语）以后说：“同志，你处在这样的环境中，凯不妙战？”可以跟本诗印证。"},{"id":"04aad98e13","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"九疑山，又名苍梧山，在湖南省南部宁远县城南60里。古代传说：尧帝有二女，名娥皇、女英，同嫁舜帝。舜南游死于苍梧，即葬其地。二妃寻舜至湘江，慎念不已，泪滴竹上而成斑点，称为湘妃竹。所以下文有“斑竹一枝千滴泪”之句。"},{"id":"83f941961a","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"帝子，即指尧帝的两个女儿嫩皇、女英。疏）。[4]翠微，轻淡青葱的山色，指“未及山顶”的高处（参见《尔雅·释山"},{"id":"cf63d0ecc9","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"雪，形容白浪。13]长岛，长沙橘子洲（见《沁园春·长沙》注），代指长沙。我欲因之梦家廊，化用李白《梦游天烤吟留别》“我欲因之梦吴越”句。芙蓉国，五代谭用之《秋宿湘江遇雨》：“秋风万里芙蓉国，雨千家薛荔村。芙蓉国是说芙蓉花到处盛开的地方，这里指湖南省。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7c32b1dffb","type":"title","text":"七律·答友人","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"17d761caab","type":"paragraph","text":"九疑山上白云飞，帝子乘风下翠微斑竹一枝干滴洞，红霞万朵百重衣。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"04aad98e13","type":"paragraph","text":"洞庭川波涌连天雪叫","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"83f941961a","type":"paragraph","text":"长岛以人歌动地诗。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"cf63d0ecc9","type":"paragraph","text":"我欲因之梦零廊，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"958e5eb9a4","type":"paragraph","text":"芙蓉国里尽朝晖。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"ce34a2d077","type":"subtitle","text":"财有美蒙来代","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"f29aea8217","type":"paragraph","text":"《芙蓉国里尽朝晖》（诗意画）","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"},{"id":"8a17e1f2f4","type":"paragraph","text":"洞庭，洞庭湖，在湖南省北部。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e"}],"page":{"id":"dfe3847ba9","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"f2fa2d3d9e","start":527,"end":528}}}},"__N_SSG":true}